   "cell_type": "raw",
   "source": "{\n \"cells\": [\n  {\n   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n   \"metadata\": {},\n   \"source\": [\n    \"# XLM-RoBERTa Fine-tuning — `career_position` Annotation\\n\",\n    \"\\n\",\n    \"Fine-tune `xlm-roberta-base` to classify job descriptions into CoREx career position codes.\\n\",\n    \"\\n\",\n    \"**Task:** annotation / `career_position`  \\n\",\n    \"**Input:** `job_description_label` (silver standard text)  \\n\",\n    \"**Output:** career position code (e.g. `401 = politics`)  \\n\",\n    \"\\n\",\n    \"XLM-RoBERTa is trained on 100 languages via masked language modelling on CommonCrawl\\n\",\n    \"and consistently outperforms mBERT on multilingual benchmarks. Since `job_description_label`\\n\",\n    \"is predominantly English but includes non-English entries (via `cv_local` fallback),\\n\",\n    \"this model is expected to be the strongest encoder baseline.\\n\",\n    \"\\n\",\n    \"**Requirements:** `pip install corex_eval[bert]`\"\n   ],\n   \"id\": \"715a33b36d074333\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n   \"metadata\": {},\n   \"source\": [\n    \"## 1. Imports & config\"\n   ],\n   \"id\": \"e56ce2d93bbc418c\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n   \"metadata\": {\n    \"ExecuteTime\": {\n     \"end_time\": \"2026-03-20T15:50:55.625325625Z\",\n     \"start_time\": \"2026-03-20T15:50:55.546285426Z\"\n    }\n   },\n   \"source\": [\n    \"from dotenv import load_dotenv\\n\",\n    \"load_dotenv()\"\n   ],\n   \"id\": \"a1c361a5391c49fd\",\n   \"outputs\": [\n    {\n     \"data\": {\n      \"text/plain\": [\n       \"True\"\n      ]\n     },\n     \"execution_count\": 1,\n     \"metadata\": {},\n     \"output_type\": \"execute_result\"\n    }\n   ],\n   \"execution_count\": 1\n  },\n  {\n   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n   \"metadata\": {\n    \"ExecuteTime\": {\n     \"end_time\": \"2026-03-20T15:50:58.514119526Z\",\n     \"start_time\": \"2026-03-20T15:50:55.627698540Z\"\n    }\n   },\n   \"source\": [\n    \"from pathlib import Path\\n\",\n    \"\\n\",\n    \"import numpy as np\\n\",\n    \"import pandas as pd\\n\",\n    \"import torch\\n\",\n    \"from transformers import (\\n\",\n    \"    AutoModelForSequenceClassification,\\n\",\n    \"    AutoTokenizer,\\n\",\n    \"    Trainer,\\n\",\n    \"    TrainingArguments,\\n\",\n    \")\\n\",\n    \"\\n\",\n    \"from corex_eval import evaluate, load_inputs, load_training_data\\n\",\n    \"\\n\",\n    \"# --- Hyperparameters ---\\n\",\n    \"MODEL_NAME   = \\\"xlm-roberta-base\\\"\\n\",\n    \"MAX_LENGTH   = 128\\n\",\n    \"EPOCHS       = 5\\n\",\n    \"BATCH_SIZE   = 32\\n\",\n    \"LR           = 2e-5\\n\",\n    \"WEIGHT_DECAY = 0.01\\n\",\n    \"WARMUP_RATIO = 0.1\\n\",\n    \"SEED         = 42\\n\",\n    \"\\n\",\n    \"OUTPUT_DIR = Path(\\\"checkpoints\\\")\\n\",\n    \"\\n\",\n    \"device = torch.device(\\\"cuda\\\" if torch.cuda.is_available() else \\\"cpu\\\")\\n\",\n    \"print(f\\\"Device: {device}\\\")\"\n   ],\n   \"id\": \"6d0eb3e5a4d04147\",\n   \"outputs\": [\n    {\n     \"name\": \"stdout\",\n     \"output_type\": \"stream\",\n     \"text\": [\n      \"Device: cuda\\n\"\n     ]\n    }\n   ],\n   \"execution_count\": 2\n  },\n  {\n   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n   \"metadata\": {},\n   \"source\": [\n    \"## 2. Load training data\"\n   ],\n   \"id\": \"882c937c7a914b87\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n   \"metadata\": {\n    \"ExecuteTime\": {\n     \"end_time\": \"2026-03-20T15:50:59.362227195Z\",\n     \"start_time\": \"2026-03-20T15:50:58.561929284Z\"\n    }\n   },\n   \"source\": \"train_df = load_training_data(\\n    task=\\\"annotation\\\",\\n    variable=\\\"career_position\\\",\\n    features=[\\\"job_description_label\\\", \\\"workplace_label\\\", \\\"career_position\\\"],\\n)\\ntrain_df = (\\n    train_df\\n    .dropna(subset=[\\\"job_description_label\\\", \\\"career_position\\\"])\\n    .pipe(lambda df: df[df[\\\"job_description_label\\\"].str.strip() != \\\"\\\"])\\n    .reset_index(drop=True)\\n)\\ntrain_df[\\\"input_text\\\"] = (\\n    train_df[\\\"job_description_label\\\"] + \\\" | \\\" + train_df[\\\"workplace_label\\\"].fillna(\\\"\\\")\\n)\\nprint(f\\\"{len(train_df)} training rows\\\")\\ntrain_df[[\\\"job_description_label\\\", \\\"workplace_label\\\", \\\"career_position\\\"]].head()\",\n   \"id\": \"253ff8e5d3d04eac\",\n   \"outputs\": [\n    {\n     \"data\": {\n      \"text/plain\": [\n       \"                   job_description_label                      workplace_label  \\\\\\n\",\n       \"0                                  Chair           Socialist Party of Albania   \\n\",\n       \"1                                  Mayor                  Tirana Municipality   \\n\",\n       \"2  Minister of Culture, Youth and Sports                Government of Albania   \\n\",\n       \"3                  Professor of painting                 Academy of Fine Arts   \\n\",\n       \"4                               Director  Department of Public Administration   \\n\",\n       \"\\n\",\n       \"                                     career_position  \\n\",\n       \"0  128 = Other political executive triangle position  \\n\",\n       \"1    414 = Executive office, local level, e.g. mayor  \\n\",\n       \"2  105 = Minister with portfolio (including Europ...  \\n\",\n       \"3  308 = Education: university (cf. higher educat...  \\n\",\n       \"4  211 = Head or deputy head of non-ministerial b...  \"\n      ],\n      \"text/html\": [\n       \"<div>\\n\",\n       \"<style scoped>\\n\",\n       \"    .dataframe tbody tr th:only-of-type {\\n\",\n       \"        vertical-align: middle;\\n\",\n       \"    }\\n\",\n       \"\\n\",\n       \"    .dataframe tbody tr th {\\n\",\n       \"        vertical-align: top;\\n\",\n       \"    }\\n\",\n       \"\\n\",\n       \"    .dataframe thead th {\\n\",\n       \"        text-align: right;\\n\",\n       \"    }\\n\",\n       \"</style>\\n\",\n       \"<table border=\\\"1\\\" class=\\\"dataframe\\\">\\n\",\n      